  "prompt": "Where in North America is area code 632?",
  "response": "As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, **area code 632 is not assigned to any specific geographic region** within the North American Numbering Plan (NANP), which encompasses the United States, Canada, and several Caribbean countries. \n\nThe NANP regularly updates and assigns new area codes as needed to accommodate population growth and increased demand for telephone numbers. If you're encountering a phone number with the area code 632, it might be:\n\n1. **A Vanity or Special Service Number:** Sometimes, specific combinations are reserved for services rather than geographic regions.\n2. **Misassigned or Incorrect:** There could be an error in the number you're referencing.\n3. **A Future Assignment:** Area codes are periodically introduced, so it's possible that 632 could be assigned in the future.\n\nFor the most accurate and up-to-date information, I recommend checking the [North American Numbering Plan Administration (NANPA)](https://www.nationalnanpa.com/) website or contacting your local telecommunications provider.",
